  "content": " `cargo test -p corvia-server -- --nocapture`\nExpected: all existing tests PASS\n\n**Step 8: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add crates/corvia-server/src/rest.rs\ngit commit -m \"feat(m3.2): REST /v1/context + /v1/ask endpoints; fix search routing through RAG\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 10: MCP Tools — corvia_context and corvia_ask\n\nAdd RAG tools to the MCP server and fix `corvia_search` routing.\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `crates/corvia-server/src/mcp.rs`\n\n**Step 1: Add tool definitions**\n\nAdd to the `tool_definitions()` vec:\n\n```rust\n        json!({\n            \"name\": \"corvia_context\",\n            \"description\": \"Retrieve and assemble organizational knowledge context for a query (no generation)\",\n            \"inputSchema\": {\n                \"type\": \"object\",\n                \"properties\": {\n                    \"query\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"The search query\" },\n                    \"scope_id\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"Scope to search within\" },\n                    \"limit\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"description\": \"Maximum sources (default 10)\" },\n                    \"expand_graph\": { \"type\": \"boolean\", \"description\": \"Follow graph edges (default true)\" }\n                },\n                \"required\": [\"query\", \"scope_id\"]\n            }\n        }),\n        json!({\n            \"name\": \"corvia_ask\",\n            \"description\": \"Ask a question and get an AI-generated answer from organizational knowledge (full RAG)\",\n            \"inputSchema\": {\n                \"type\": \"object\",\n                \"properties\": {\n                    \"query\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"The question to answer\" },\n                    \"scope_id\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"Scope to search within\" },\n                    \"limit\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"description\": \"Maximum sources (default 10)\" },\n                    \"expand_graph\": { \"type\": \"boolean\", \"description\": \"Follow graph edges (default true)\" }\n                },\n                \"required\": [\"query\", \"scope_id\"]\n            }\n        }),\n```\n\n**Step 2: Add tool dispatch**",
